<TEXT>
The approach of 1993 and the formal creation of the single European market
has prompted the organisers of this year's National Small Firms Policy and
Research Conference to hold part of the event in France.
The conference, the largest annual get-together of academics specialising in
small firms research, will start in Southampton on November 25 and 26 and,
